title: Complete Electric Wizard Discography
description:
This is a complete Electric Wizard Discography I&#039;ve compiled from others. It mainly came from one torrent that had both Electric Wizard and Orange Goblin together. They were missing Witchcult Today, so I wanted to make a more complete one.

Contents
=========
1995 - Electric Wizard
1997 - Chrono.naut-Nuclear Guru (split Electric Wizard & Orange Goblin)
1997 - Come My Fanatics 
1998 - Supercoven
2000 - Dopethrone  
2002 - Let Us Prey
2004 - We Live 
2006 - Pre-Electric Wizard 1989 - 1994
2007 - Witchcult Today

Extras
-(2001) Live In Philadelphia 04.03.2001
-(2005) Live at BBC Maida Vale Studio
-(2005) Live At Roaburn
-Live Iowa City

Majority of songs are 320 bit-rate mp3s, but most of the live ones are 128. This is my first torrent, but I hope everything is set up properly and everyone enjoys!
